hed in a political process productive of both authority and dissent.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aElite (Social sciences)zChinaxHistoryy20th century. 0aPolitical activistszChinavBiography. 0aPolitical culturezChinaxHistoryy20th century. 0aPolitical leadershipzChinaxHistoryy20th century. 0aPolitical oratoryzChinaxHistoryy20th century. 7aHISTORY / Asia / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013z978311069042240uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052094874740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520948747423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520948747/original  a978-3-11-069042-2  University of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles